            "content": "# Apps\n\nThe monorepo ships eight deployable applications:\n\n| App | Stack | Role |\n|-----|-------|------|\n| [`cli`](./cli/index.md) | Bun + TypeScript + Ink | Primary developer interface (`droid` command) |\n| [`daemon`](./daemon.md) | Bun + TypeScript | Background process managing agent sessions |\n| [`backend`](./backend/index.md) | Next.js 15 | REST API, LLM proxy, auth, billing |\n| [`web`](./web.md) | Vite + React | Browser-based Droid interface |\n| [`desktop`](./desktop.md) | Electron | Native desktop app wrapping web + daemon |\n| [`relay`](./relay.md) | Bun + TypeScript | WebSocket relay for BYOI/BYOK machines |\n| [`signal`](./signal.md) | GCP Cloud Function | Session analytics and friction detection |\n| `functions` | Firebase | Serverless backend functions |\n\nThe `factory-vscode-extension` and `factory-jetbrains-plugin` are editor extensions that integrate with the Factory platform.\n\n## Communication topology\n\n```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    CLI[\"CLI (droid)\"] -->|\"JSON-RPC\"| Daemon\n    Web[\"apps/web\"] -->|\"WebSocket JSON-RPC\"| Daemon\n    Desktop[\"apps/desktop\"] -->|\"WebSocket JSON-RPC\"| Daemon\n    Daemon -->|\"HTTPS\"| Backend[\"apps/backend\"]\n    Web -->|\"BYOI path\"| Relay[\"apps/relay\"]\n    Relay -->|\"WebSocket\"| Daemon\n```\n\nThe daemon is the central hub on each machine. Both the CLI (via stdin/stdout) and browser clients (via WebSocket) communicate through it to reach the backend.\n",
