            "content": "# Deployment\n\nFactory has multiple deployable units, each with its own CI/CD pipeline.\n\n## Deployable units\n\n| Service | Platform | Workflow |\n|---------|----------|---------|\n| `apps/backend` | Vercel | `deploy-prod.yml`, `deploy-dev-web.yml` |\n| `apps/web` | Vercel | same as backend |\n| `apps/admin` | Vercel | `deploy-prod-admin.yml` |\n| `apps/cli` | S3 + npm | `cli-release.yml`, `cli-release-npm.yml` |\n| `apps/daemon` | S3 | `factoryd-release.yml` |\n| `apps/desktop` | S3 + auto-update | `desktop-release.yml` |\n| `apps/relay` | AWS (ECS/Lambda) | `deploy-relay-aws.yml` |\n| `apps/signal` | GCP Cloud Functions | `signal-deploy.yml` |\n| `apps/functions` | Firebase | Firebase deploy |\n\n## Pages in this section\n\n- [CI/CD](./ci-cd.md) — GitHub Actions workflows and what they do\n- [Release process](./release-process.md) — how versions are cut and distributed\n",
