            "content": "# Configuration\n\n## CLI configuration\n\nThe CLI reads configuration from several sources, in priority order:\n\n1. **Environment variables** (highest priority)\n2. **`.env.local`** in `apps/cli/` (local overrides, gitignored)\n3. **`.env`** in `apps/cli/` (default config)\n4. **User settings** (stored via `@factory/runtime`, read by `SettingsService`)\n\nKey CLI environment variables:\n\n| Variable | Default | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `FACTORY_API_URL` | `https://api.factory.ai` | Backend API base URL |\n| `FACTORY_ENV` | `production` | `production`, `development`, `staging` |\n| `FACTORYD_PORT` | `37643` | Daemon port to connect to |\n| `FACTORY_OTEL_ENABLED` | `false` | Enable OpenTelemetry tracing |\n\n## Daemon configuration\n\nThe daemon reads from `apps/daemon/.env` and `.env.local`:\n\n| Variable | Default | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `FACTORY_ENV` | `production` | Deployment environment |\n| `FACTORYD_HOST` | `127.0.0.1` | Host to bind |\n| `FACTORYD_PORT` | `37643` | Port to listen on (41723 in dev) |\n| `FACTORYD_DISABLE_AUTO_UPDATE` | `false` | Disable auto-update (used by Electron) |\n| `FACTORY_OTEL_ENABLED` | `false` | Enable OTEL distributed tracing |\n\n## Backend configuration\n\n`apps/backend/.env` and `.env.local`:\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| `WORKOS_API_KEY` | WorkOS API key |\n| `WORKOS_CLIENT_ID` | WorkOS client ID |\n| `NEXT_PUBLIC_WORKOS_CLIENT_ID` | WorkOS client ID (client-side) |\n| `FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_*` | Firebase credentials |\n| `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` | Anthropic API key (for LLM proxy) |\n| `OPENAI_API_KEY` | OpenAI API key |\n| `GOOGLE_API_KEY` | Google AI API key |\n| `ORB_API_KEY` | Orb billing API key |\n| `STATSIG_SERVER_KEY` | Statsig server SDK key |\n| `SENTRY_DSN` | Sentry error tracking DSN |\n| `AWS_*` | AWS credentials (for S3, bug reports) |\n\n## Relay configuration\n\n| Variable | Default | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `FACTORY_RELAY_PORT` | `8080` | Port to listen on |\n| `FACTORY_RELAY_HOST` | `0.0.0.0` | Bind host |\n| `FACTORY_RELAY_DEBUG` | `false` | Debug logging |\n\n## Feature flags\n\nFeature flags are managed via Statsig. Definitions live in `packages/common/src/feature-flags/constants.ts`. The Statsig project/console is the source of truth for which flags are enabled in which environments.\n\n## TypeScript configuration\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `tsconfig.json` (root) | Base compiler options for all workspaces |\n| `tsconfig.next.json` (root) | Next.js-specific overrides |\n| `apps/*/tsconfig.json` | Per-app overrides |\n| `packages/*/tsconfig.json` | Per-package overrides |\n| `apps/*/tsconfig.build.json` | Build-time configs (stricter, no test files) |\n\nPath aliases:\n- `@/` → `src/` within each app/package\n- `@factory/*` → `packages/*` (resolved by npm workspaces)\n",
