            "content": "# Data models\n\nKey data structures used throughout the system. Type sources are in `packages/common/src/` unless noted.\n\n## Session\n\nThe central domain object. Stored in Firestore.\n\n```ts\n// packages/common/src/session/\ninterface Session {\n  sessionId: string;\n  title: string;\n  ownerId: string;\n  orgId: string;\n  createdAt: string;        // ISO timestamp\n  updatedAt: string;\n  workingDirectory: string;\n  droidConfig: DroidConfig;\n  messageTree: MessageTree;\n  tags: string[];\n  status: SessionStatus;    // 'active' | 'archived'\n}\n```\n\n## Message\n\nA single entry in the session's message history.\n\n```ts\ninterface Message {\n  messageId: string;\n  sessionId: string;\n  role: 'user' | 'assistant' | 'tool';\n  content: string | ContentBlock[];\n  toolCalls?: ToolCall[];\n  toolResults?: ToolResult[];\n  createdAt: string;\n  model?: string;           // LLM model used (for assistant messages)\n  usage?: TokenUsage;       // Token counts for billing\n}\n```\n\n## Tool call and result\n\n```ts\ninterface ToolCall {\n  toolCallId: string;\n  name: string;             // e.g., 'Read', 'Execute'\n  input: Record<string, unknown>;\n}\n\ninterface ToolResult {\n  toolCallId: string;\n  content: string;\n  isError: boolean;\n}\n```\n\n## Droid configuration\n\n```ts\n// packages/common/src/droid/\ninterface DroidConfig {\n  droidId: string;\n  name: string;\n  systemPrompt?: string;\n  tools: string[];           // tool names enabled for this droid\n  model: string;             // LLM model identifier\n}\n```\n\n## Feature flag definition\n\n```ts\n// packages/common/src/feature-flags/constants.ts\ninterface FeatureFlagDefinition {\n  displayName: string;\n  statsigName: string;       // must match the Statsig console name\n  defaultValue: boolean;\n}\n```\n\n## LLM request\n\n```ts\n// packages/droid-core/src/llms/types.ts\ninterface LLMRequest {\n  model: string;\n  messages: LLMMessage[];\n  tools?: ToolSchema[];\n  maxTokens?: number;\n  temperature?: number;\n  stream: true;\n}\n```\n\n## Daemon config\n\n```ts\n// packages/daemon-core/src/types.ts\ninterface DaemonCoreConfig {\n  port: number;\n  host: string;\n  shell: string;\n  homeDir: string;\n  apiBaseUrl: string;\n  deploymentEnv: string;\n  isProductionTier: boolean;\n}\n```\n\n## Relay envelope\n\n```ts\n// packages/common/src/relay/\ninterface RelayEnvelope {\n  clientId: string;\n  computerId: string;\n  payload: string;           // JSON-serialized JSON-RPC message\n}\n```\n\n## Organization\n\n```ts\n// packages/common/src/organization/\ninterface Organization {\n  orgId: string;\n  name: string;\n  plan: 'free' | 'pro' | 'enterprise';\n  createdAt: string;\n  memberCount: number;\n}\n```\n",
