            "content": "# External dependencies\n\nKey third-party services and libraries used by the Factory platform.\n\n## External services\n\n| Service | Purpose | Used by |\n|---|---|---|\n| **WorkOS** | Authentication and user management | `apps/backend`, CLI |\n| **Firestore** | Primary database | `apps/backend` |\n| **Vercel** | Hosting for web apps | `apps/backend`, `apps/web`, `apps/admin` |\n| **Anthropic** | Claude LLM models | Backend LLM proxy, CLI (BYOK) |\n| **OpenAI** | GPT and o-series models | Backend LLM proxy, CLI (BYOK) |\n| **Google GenAI** | Gemini models | Backend LLM proxy, CLI (BYOK) |\n| **Orb** | Usage-based billing | `apps/backend` |\n| **Statsig** | Feature flags | `apps/backend`, all frontend apps |\n| **Sentry** | Error tracking | All apps |\n| **E2B** | Cloud development environments (CDEs) | `apps/backend` |\n| **Exa** | Web search API | `apps/backend`, `packages/droid-core` |\n| **Slack** | Notifications and integrations | `apps/backend` |\n| **GitHub** | Repository integration | `apps/backend`, `packages/droid-core` |\n| **Linear** | Issue tracking integration | `apps/backend` |\n| **Segment** | Product analytics | `apps/backend` |\n| **Loops** | Email automation | `apps/backend` |\n| **Axiom** | Log aggregation and analytics | `apps/backend`, `apps/daemon` |\n| **S3** | Binary distribution and bug reports | `apps/backend`, CLI, daemon |\n| **Firebase Functions** | Serverless background tasks | `apps/functions` |\n\n## Key npm packages\n\n### LLM and AI\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `@anthropic-ai/sdk` | — | Anthropic API client |\n| `openai` | `^6.25.0` | OpenAI API client |\n| `@google/genai` | `1.31.0` | Google GenAI client |\n| `@modelcontextprotocol/sdk` | `^1.26.0` | MCP protocol SDK |\n\n### Frontend\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `react`, `react-dom` | UI framework (v19) |\n| `styled-components` | CSS-in-JS styling |\n| `redux-toolkit` | State management |\n| `@workos-inc/authkit-react` | WorkOS authentication |\n| `ink` | React-based terminal renderer (v6.7.0) |\n| `commander` | CLI argument parsing |\n\n### Backend\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `next` | Next.js framework (v15) |\n| `firebase-admin` | Firestore server SDK |\n| `@workos-inc/node` | WorkOS server SDK |\n| `orb-billing` | Orb billing client |\n| `@statsig/statsig-node-core` | Statsig server SDK |\n| `@sentry/nextjs` | Sentry for Next.js |\n\n### Infrastructure\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `turbo` | Monorepo build orchestration |\n| `bun` | JavaScript runtime for CLI and daemon |\n| `tsx` | TypeScript execution (dev mode) |\n| `knip` | Unused export detection |\n| `husky` | Git hooks |\n\n### Testing\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `jest` | Primary test framework |\n| `vitest` | Test framework for `packages/frontend` |\n| `@testing-library/react` | React testing utilities |\n| `@microsoft/tui-test` | TUI E2E testing |\n| `playwright` | Browser E2E testing |\n\n## Version constraints\n\nKey version constraints from root `package.json` overrides:\n\n```json\n\"overrides\": {\n  \"ink\": \"6.7.0\",\n  \"cookie@<0.7.0\": \"0.7.0\"\n}\n```\n\nThe `ink` version is pinned because the TUI rendering depends on specific behavior in v6.7.0.\n",
