            "content": "# Getting started\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- Node.js 18.x (see `.nvmrc`)\n- npm 11.x (the monorepo uses `packageManager: \"npm@11.2.0\"`)\n- Bun 1.3.x (for CLI, daemon, and relay)\n- Git\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/Factory-AI/factory-mono.git\ncd factory-mono\nnpm install\n```\n\n`npm install` runs `npm run setup` automatically via the `postinstall` hook, which runs `turbo run setup` across all packages.\n\n## Running the web stack\n\n```bash\n# Starts: backend (port 3000), web (port 3002), admin (port 3001), storybook, daemon\nnpm run dev:web\n\n# Starts the same set but with Electron instead of daemon (macOS only)\nnpm run dev:desktop\n```\n\nDo not run `npm run dev` at the root — it is disabled intentionally.\n\nEach app streams its output to both console and a log file:\n\n| App | Log file |\n|-----|----------|\n| backend | `/tmp/factory-dev-backend.log` |\n| admin | `/tmp/factory-dev-admin.log` |\n| desktop | `/tmp/factory-dev-desktop.log` |\n| daemon | `/tmp/factory-dev-daemon.log` |\n\n## CLI development\n\n```bash\n# Build CLI and create droid-dev and droid-localhost wrappers\ncd apps/cli && npm run setup\n\n# Run against hosted dev API\ndroid-dev\n\n# Run against local API (localhost:3000)\ndroid-localhost\n```\n\nAfter any CLI or daemon code change, rebuild the CLI and restart the daemon.\n\n## Build\n\n```bash\nnpm run build               # Build all packages\nnpm run build -- --filter=apps/web   # Build only web app\n```\n\n## Testing\n\n```bash\nnpm run test -- --filter=@factory/common   # Run tests for one package\nnpm run test -- --filter=@factory/daemon-core --filter=@factory/droid-core\n```\n\nRun a single test file:\n\n```bash\ncd apps/backend && npx jest path/to/file.test.ts\ncd packages/frontend && npx vitest run path/to/file.test.ts\n```\n\nFrontend E2E tests use Playwright:\n\n```bash\ncd packages/frontend && npm run test:e2e\ncd packages/frontend && npm run test:e2e -- --headed --debug\n```\n\n## Type checking and linting\n\n```bash\nnpm run typecheck           # TypeScript across all packages\nnpm run fix                 # Lint + format (preferred over npm run lint)\nnpm run lint                # Lint only\n```\n\nAlways use `--` before `--filter` when passing flags to turbo scripts:\n\n```bash\n# Correct\nnpm run test -- --filter=@factory/common\n\n# Wrong — npm eats the flag and turbo runs everything\nnpm run test --filter=@factory/common\n```\n\n## Ports\n\n| App | Port |\n|-----|------|\n| Backend API | 3000 |\n| Admin dashboard | 3001 |\n| Web app | 3002 |\n| Daemon (production) | 37643 |\n| Daemon (development) | 41723 |\n\n## Log locations\n\n| Environment | Directory |\n|-------------|-----------|\n| Production | `~/.factory/logs/` |\n| Development | `~/.factory-dev/logs/` |\n\nKey log files: `factoryd.log`, `droid-log-single.log`, `console.log`.\n\n## Related pages\n\n- [Architecture](./architecture.md) — understand how the pieces connect before developing\n- [Daemon debugging](./domains/daemon.md#debugging) — troubleshooting CLI/daemon/frontend communication\n",
